TestMockInterceptDownstreamVariableAnnotatesAsMock
/ mock.intercept write-target annotates as (mock) downstream — not (object).
/ Stage 2 typed mock.intercept as Task<Data<Mock.@this>> — the reflected
/ return type flows through goal.getTypes into the next step's snapshot.
- builder.goals from 'probes/mock/', write to %goals%
- goal.getTypes %goals[0]%, write to %snapshot%
- set %annot% = %snapshot[1].m%
- assert.equals expected='mock', actual=%annot%
